# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .trivyignore — StagePass Seat Inventory Service
#
# RULE-21: Every suppression must include:
#   - CVE ID and affected package@version
#   - Reason: why it is not exploitable in this specific usage
#   - Expires: review date (max 6 months from suppression date)
#
# Format:
#   # CVE-YYYY-NNNNN (package@version)
#   # Reason: ...
#   # Expires: YYYY-MM-DD
#   CVE-YYYY-NNNNN
#
# DO NOT suppress CRITICAL CVEs without written justification reviewed
# by a second engineer. This file is reviewed as part of Phase 8 hardening.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# No suppressions at scaffold time.
# Add entries here as they arise, with full justification per RULE-21.
