#
# # CVE-2025-12345 (some-library@1.2.3)
# # Reason: Vulnerability requires unauthenticated HTTP endpoint. This service
# #         has no REST surface — only gRPC (port 9090, NetworkPolicy restricted)
# #         and Actuator (port 8090, internal only). The attack vector is not
# #         reachable in our deployment topology.
# # Expires: 2026-12-01
